headline: Starbucks (SBUX) Declares Quarterly Dividend of US$0.61 Per Share
summary: Starbucks (SBUX) recently affirmed its commitment to value by maintaining a cash dividend of $0.61 per share, reflecting its ongoing focus on shareholder returns. headline: Starbucks hit with Street-low price target, Opendoor surges
summary: Julie Hyman examines what's driving interest in two top stories on Wall Street in Yahoo Finance's Market Minute. Starbucks (SBUX) was downgraded to Underperform by Jefferies. The analysts also gave the stock a Street-low price target of $76, citing weak consumer spending and costs associated with ongoing turnaround efforts. Real-estate platform Opendoor Technologies (OPEN) stock is surging after activist investor Eric Jackson expressed a bullish stance on the stock. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
